One night they had a dream: they saw the blessed martyr coming to them, and a spotless lamb was at her side. She told them of the glory which she had attained in heaven. This appearance is commemorated in the Latin Church on the 28th of J anuary, and hence sheis generally represented with a lamb standing near her. Her martyrdom has been celebrated on the 21st os January, since the fourth age, and by the whole Catholic Church.
